{"tid":1085784,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"勸下大家叫pizza唔好再用外判外賣公司","createTime":"2019-03-31T11:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T10:41:52.000Z","uid":224836,"like":64,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"19485eacfcdc69a3bcc73abcfac0f4c912aeb675","tid":1085784,"uid":224836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"唔好用deliveroo/food panda叫pizza啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從外賣仔角度出發：因為呢啲單多數好大單好多野拎 而且餐廳等候時間長 十個有九個都會踢單唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果餐廳就做好食物 但就無人去接單送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食物去到可能凍哂又唔好食 而且遲到客人又會嬲嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n從客人角度出發：我自己都試過用其中一間叫pizza食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7點下單 9點幾先有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係餓死都未有得食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食物到左 但已經凍凍地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以依加想食pizza都係直接打電話去pizza hut/其他店下單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 起碼佢地有專用車手送單<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食左咁多次啲野食都係熱辣辣咁到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b305bb7b727f971b9bfd170803bea759cc3312","tid":1085784,"uid":21423,"like":9,"dislike":19,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:57:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2dbdd95f716340146edd335ed83a8bbc26def4ef","tid":1085784,"uid":89558,"like":10,"dislike":17,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20